Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击国会大厦的罪魁祸首\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the attack of the Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经身处狼穴了  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The jackals are at the door, Mr. President.
