Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的首席探员失踪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your lead investigator is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试图杀你的人依旧活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The man who tried to kill you is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宫里的叛徒身份依然成谜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the mole in the White House remains unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要解除你的权力  即刻生效\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am relieving you of your command, effective immediately.
