Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也杀你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I kill yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.91,0:00:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jason...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏效了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all working.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人的注意力都在联调局那边  而非我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone's focused on the FBI, not us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉娜在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is Hannah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出外勤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开所有的集装箱进行搜索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want every container opened and searched.
