Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手放在脑后  手放在脑后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get your hands behind your head! Hands behind your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跪在地上  快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the ground right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手举过头顶  跪下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hands above your head! Get on your knees!
