Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:01:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跪下  我不会再说第二次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said get on the ground! I'm not gonna ask you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退后  不然我就引爆炸弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get back, or I'll detonate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退后  不然我就炸了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get back, or I'll blow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.15,0:01:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把枪放下  我是认真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put your guns down! I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停  不准开火  退后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop. Nobody fires. Get back!
