Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快追\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去后面  上楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go back! Up the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动  让我看到你的双手  别动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Freeze! Let me see your hands! Hold it right there!
