Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经说过了  我跟这事没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I already told you -- I had nothing to do with this.
