Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是才怪  放了她  -谁授命的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The hell she is. Let her go. - Under whose authority?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得和真的似的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统想要马上见她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wants her in his office ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹  白宫打给我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dan, I got the White House on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说什么来着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们杀了杰森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They killed Jason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得向总统汇报我们所了解的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, we have to tell the president what we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想陷害我发动恐袭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They wanted to blame me for an attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们伪造了放在我公寓里的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so they planted evidence in my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们通知了联调局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They called the FBI,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们我带着炸弹去了车库\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}said that I'd be in the garage with a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在审问从货轮上抓到的嫌疑人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're interrogating the suspects that we arrested on the freighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们供出了窝点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're giving up Intel on the cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳埃德那边怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about Lloyd?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找到的唯一联系是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only link that we've managed to find
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,货轮归布朗宁·里德旗下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is between the ship and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一间已倒闭的子公司所有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a defunct subsidiary of Browning Reed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证据还不够充分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not a smoking gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎样  汤姆  你得逮捕那混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what? You need to bring that bastard in, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I agree, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能定他罪的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no point in bringing him in today
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓他根本没有意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if we have to let him out tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得像对付麦克利什那样对付他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to play this the same way that we did MacLeish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, look how that turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我同意他们的观点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I agree with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是现在我们不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Especially given the fact that we don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宫里面的叛徒是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who the traitor is in the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去抓他吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的目标是帕特里克·劳埃德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our target is Patrick Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为他是国会爆炸案的幕后主使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We believe that he is responsible for the bombing on our Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在住在位于弗吉尼亚州沃伦顿西边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He currently resides on a 100-acre horse farm
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一处100英亩的养马场里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}west of Warrenton, Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要假定他全副武装\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should assume he is heavily armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他杀了我们的朋友  杀了我们的领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He killed our friends, and he killed our leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要活捉他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will take him alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并让他对我们的所作所为付出代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we will make him pay for everything he took from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都清楚了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is everyone clear on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清楚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我们出发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Let's move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯克曼政府存在着联调局阴谋吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there an FBI conspiracy in the Kirkman Administration?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这令人感到不安  奈特  十分不安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's very concerning, Nate -- very concerning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前的已知信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, what we now know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使我们对总统所说的一切都产生了怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it casts doubt on everything the president has ever told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还怎么能信任他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are we supposed to trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么消息了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What have you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前我们已确认位于蒙大纳  亚利桑那\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So far, we've identified cells in Montana, Arizona,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宾州  新泽西和新墨西哥州的窝点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pennsylvania, New Jersey, and New Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局的境内威胁联合反恐部队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, the FBI's Joint Terrorism Task Force on Domestic Threats
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已派小队前往这些地点以便协调突击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is moving teams into position so we can coordinate the raids,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避免惊动他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not tip them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我读了他们的宣言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I read their "manifesto."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太荒唐了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们引用的历史警句恰到好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They use just the right amount of historical quotes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以试图正当化自己的所作所为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to try and make themselves sound legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这与党派无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're not political.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是对权力的攫取  一场未遂的政变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a power grab -- an attempted coup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳埃德那边处理得怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are we at with Lloyd?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战术部队已经出发了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tactical team's en route.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很快就能将他拿下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll have him in custody within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一有消息立刻通知我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want updates as soon as they come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  法索局长  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great work, Director Foerstel. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这论点很出彩  鲍曼议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's an excellent argument, Senator Bowman,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得下一位嘉宾可能会反对你的观点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm sure my next guest will probably disagree --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}联调局掩盖了真相吗  柯克曼沉默了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有请白宫前幕僚长亚伦·肖尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}recent White House chief of staff Aaron Shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  奈特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Nate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想对担心存在政府阴谋论的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what do you say to all the Americans out there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国人民说些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who are worried about a government conspiracy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会说柯克曼总统大概是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd say that President Kirkman is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识的人里面最诚实的一位了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}probably the most honest man I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你和鲍曼议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I think you and Senator Bowman
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都试图将国家安全问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are both trying to score political points
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成自己的政治筹码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}over matters of national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说报道是假的吗  肖尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you saying this story isn't true, then, Mr. Shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说我了解得并不全面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm saying I haven't been fully briefed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议员也是一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and neither has the senator,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们中没有一个人有权作出指控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so neither one of us should be making any kind of accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但事实是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the fact remains --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果涉及了国家安全问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if these are matters of national security,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统就应该向公众澄清\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the president should just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但至今他什么也没说  这令局势很不利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But so far, he's said nothing. That's a disservice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常了解总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Knowing the president as well as I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}没人有权作出指控
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确信即使他的确隐瞒了某些事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure if he's holding on to any kind of secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是为了全美国民众的安危着想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's for the safety of the American people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说有人在帮倒忙  那也是你才对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If anyone is doing a disservice here, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请大家明天继续收看本节目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay tuned tomorrow, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个故事没有完结\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This story's not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我是摩尔  -我是威尔士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Moore. - It's Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到劳埃德了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have eyes on Lloyd?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了  他还在房子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, he's still in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原位等待  我们在路上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold your position. We're en route.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}洛萨诺已拿到包裹  一切就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:08:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔士探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agent Wells!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里没人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All clear here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我一份布朗宁·里德和其子公司名下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want a list of every plane, truck, car, ship, helicopter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有飞机  卡车  汽车和直升机的清单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}registered to Browning Reed or their subsidiaries,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且要立刻追踪到位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I want it tracked now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调动联邦航管局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That means FAA,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-州机动车辆管理局  -威尔士探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- it means state DMV, - Agent Wells!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,线上搜索  当地执法部门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it means ATL, law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论用什么手段  马上给我查清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever you have to do, you get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-威尔士探员  -什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Agent Wells. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗吉尼亚州的高速公路巡警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Virginia highway patrol said
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了一辆登记在劳埃德名下的车辆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they spotted a vehicle registered to Lloyd
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在沿州际公路南行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}driving south on the interstate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开对讲机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open the walkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔士探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agent Wells!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特里克·劳埃德在切萨皮克的交通临检处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got a Patrick Lloyd sighting at a traffic stop in Chesapeake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运输安全局的人说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}TSA says they got eyes on him
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在罗利达勒姆国际机场看到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}over at Raleigh-Durham International.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又有报告说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're now saying his credit card was just used
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刚刚在匹兹堡的汽车站使用过信用卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at a bus station in Pittsburgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查到他的银行卡  在德克萨斯州的布兰诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got a hit on his ATM card -- in Plano, Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shell game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去他妈的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在问  下一次的汇报是什么时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone's asking - when the next briefing is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我有料可以爆给他们之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, until I can give them something more than a "No comment,"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要尽可能地回避媒体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna stay away from the press for as long as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情进展还顺利吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's that working out for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要开始锁办公室的门了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm gonna start locking my office door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锁门也阻碍不了我  相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, that's not gonna slow me down. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:09:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么  埃布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want, Abe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想得到白宫的回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A White House comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经回应了你的报道  那就是无可奉告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I already gave your story a "no comment."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对话是不是似曾相识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Haven't we done this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉这像是  旧事重演\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel like it's, like, "Groundhog Day" with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔萨卡是过去的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Al-Sakar was yesterday's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的是将于明天刊登的报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm talking - about tomorrow's edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次"无可奉告"可派不上用场了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A "No comment" Is not gonna cut it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那的确是部好电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a good movie, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}groundhog day亦指电影《偷天情缘》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得和你说点紧要事  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Major flag for you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃布·莱纳德在写一篇报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abe Leonard is running a story claiming
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称联调局副局长杰森·亚特伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that FBI Deputy Director Jason Atwood
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在总统办公室里因谋杀马吉德·纳萨尔被捕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was arrested in the Oval for the murder of Majid Nassar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说白宫把这消息封锁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He says the White House covered it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我要怎样回应他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, how do you want to respond to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟莱纳德先生说我想见他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell Mr. Leonard I want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安排个会议  我要和他面对面谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Set up a meeting -- face-to-face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打不通他电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't get through to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要解决掉莱纳德·埃布的报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's needs to address the Abe Leonard story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你想汤姆表现得像一个政治家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you want Tom to behave like a politician,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样他就不再是他自己了  艾米丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but that's just not who he is, Emily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是美国总统  艾丽克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is the president of the United States, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要为白宫争辩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He needs to defend the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  他会按他自己的方式来做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I know, and he will -- in his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会在这里待多久  约个午餐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long are you in town for? I miss our lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚就要回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got to head back tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备跟朋友在海亚当斯酒店随便吃点东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just gonna grab a bite with a friend at The Hay-Adams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  艾米丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, Emily?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是怎样逃掉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did he get by us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是那叛徒通风报信的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The working theory is that the traitor tipped him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幸的是  我们至今还无法找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, unfortunately, we're still no closer to finding him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要冻结他的资产  榨干那混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to freeze his assets -- bleed the son of a bitch dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联系财政部  我们要起草一项行政命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Contact Treasury. We'll have an executive order drafted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是的  总统先生  -谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes, sir. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每位总统都要处理一个重大危机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every president has a defining crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而汤姆  你有好几个呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You, Tom, have had several.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你会经受住这次危机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you are going to weather this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不管怎样  事情都将接近尾声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because one way or another, it's all coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而与此同时呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为冲击做好准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brace for impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少这方面我越来越得心应手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, at least I'm getting better at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}华盛顿白宫\N网络连接提示\N正在建立安全连接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}需要密码  区分大小写
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}保密IP路由网络
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是里特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ritter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是恰克  立刻接通汉娜办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Chuck. Get to Hannah's office now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}马克\N法雷尔\N美国海军\N中尉\N无限期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美国军警部门\N法雷尔  马克\N中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得上次的入侵事件吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, remember the hack
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用来传送马吉德·纳萨尔的视频那次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that was used to deliver the Majid Nassar video?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得  毁了白宫西翼一半的电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. That attack destroyed half the computers in the West Wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也留下了一个重要的数据痕迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Also left behind a serious digital footprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么假设\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, working under the assumption
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个内鬼也是那次入侵事件的罪魁祸首\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that our traitor was responsible for that hack, as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在密切关注同一个代码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been keeping an eye out for that same code
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防再次有人使用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in case it was used again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个内鬼刚刚进入了保密IP路由网络\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our traitor just accessed SIPRNET.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五角大楼吗  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Pentagon? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不知道  -他没进入主机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't know. - He's not in the mainframes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来他只是想创建一个身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like he just wanted to create an I.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给谁用的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An I.D. for who?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}法雷尔  马克\N中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  亚伦·肖尔来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir? Aaron Shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  艾娃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Ava.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦  很高兴再次见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aaron. Great to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我也是  总统先生  -请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You as well, sir. - Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.86,0:14:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早前我在电视上看到你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw you on television earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很感激你说的那番话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I really appreciated what you had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我会一直保护你的  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know I'll always protect you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  所以我才叫你来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know, which is why I've asked you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将要和你说的事非常机密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I'm about to tell you is strictly classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们知道白宫里有内鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We know that there's a traitor in the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直没能确定他的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We haven't been able to identify him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们知道他和国会爆炸案有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we know he was involved in the Capitol bombing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我被任命为指定幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and was instrumental in having me appointed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也起到了推动作用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as the Designated Survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾是总统里士满的幕僚之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were part of President Richmond's staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道有可能会是谁吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you have any idea who this could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说不是兰登吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, it wasn't Langdon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登已经被关押了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Langdon's in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在找的这个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The person we're looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在销毁此次阴谋的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is actively destroying evidence of the conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道一下子很难接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know this is a lot to take in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我希望你仔细看看你的记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I would like you to go back over your records,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看有什么引人注意的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}see if anything stands out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦  我们时间不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aaron, we don't have a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上去查  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll get right to it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他给洛萨诺创建了一个身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He created an I.D. for Lozano
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他能进入五角大楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to access the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得立刻提醒五角大楼保安局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to alert Pentagon Force Protection right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经做了  我们把他的照片传了过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's already done. We've sent over his picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们正在封锁大楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're locking the building down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  但五角大楼占地583英亩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but the Pentagon's 583 acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有大把地方可以藏身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That gives him plenty of places to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱纳德先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Leonard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是汤姆·柯克曼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom Kirkman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛斯和我说了你想报道的新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, Seth told me about the story you wanted to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  如果你想劝我收手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, if you think you're gonna get me to back down,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是在浪费时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你派多少人来盯我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you can send all the goons you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我绝不保持沉默\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm not staying silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't know exactly what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没派人干过这种事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I haven't sent anyone anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上  我和联调局说得很清楚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, I've been perfectly clear with the FBI --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不容许恐吓新闻媒体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not tolerate any intimidation of the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且很显然  如果我愿意的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Besides, apparently, if I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以直接把你送进监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can just throw you in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在威胁我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you threatening me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  恰恰相反\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. The opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想告诉你  我不会这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to tell you that I won't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会强迫你干任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not gonna try and make you do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在请求你  拜托先别报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am asking you -- please, just hold your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指报道有误吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you saying it's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不完整\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不如你帮我补充完整吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well...how about you fill in the blanks for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望我可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗憾的是  事关国家安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unfortunately, it's a matter of national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能问你个问题吗  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I ask you a question, Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你手握证据显示现政府有所隐瞒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you were sitting on a story about a government cover-up,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还会相信总统所说的话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}would you trust a word the president said?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许不会吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你真的相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But do you honestly believe
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:18:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若总统故意掩盖事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if a president was involved in a cover-up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还会蠢到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that he'd be stupid enough
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像现在这样与记者面对面交谈吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to sit across from a journalist such as yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最敬仰的总统是富兰克林·罗斯福\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My favorite president is Franklin Roosevelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想给你看点东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得这照片是什么时候拍的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When do you think this picture was taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜是战时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I expect during the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道它是什么时候公布的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any idea when it was published?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统过世后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just after the president passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  战争期间有这么一种共识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see, during the war, there was an understanding --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展现美国的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was more important to project American strength
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比报道总统的弱点更重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than describe the president's frailties.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媒体早就拿到了照片  但他们选择不去报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The press had the photos, but they chose not to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你认为现在并非战争期间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, you might not think that we're in a war,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我可以保证  这就是场战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I promise you that we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你发表了那篇文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and if you publish that article,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会让我们更难取胜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's going to make it that much more difficult for us to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真心希望能把知道的事告诉你  但我不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I honestly wish I could tell you what I know, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So...here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得作出选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're gonna have to make a choice --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你是否相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whether you believe me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科克兰将军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}General Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是来修电缆的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well. You're not the cable repairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退休生活怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you handling retirement?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是退休\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是软禁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's house arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让柯克曼别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you didn't leave Kirkman a choice there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不怪柯克曼  他做了他应该做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't blame Kirkman. He did what he had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不像你啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's quite the reversal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想法是会变的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Opinions change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来干什么  亚伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here, Aaron?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宫里有一个内鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a traitor in the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在调查所有拥有高级权限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm looking into anyone with high-level access
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并参与了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who had any involvement
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择指定幸存者的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in choosing the Designated Survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的人并不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not a long list.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮忙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在白宫任职八年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You served eight years in the White House --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:20:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待过国安委  武装部  参谋长联席会议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}NSC, military office, Joint Chiefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人比你更了解安全权限的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one knows more about security access than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要这些系统立即恢复使用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need these systems back online right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五角大楼保卫局  我是鲍威尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pentagon Force Protection. This is Powell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是联调局探员汉娜·威尔士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is FBI Agent Hannah Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们找到洛扎诺了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you found Lozano yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  而且我们的安全系统出现了故障\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. And we're having trouble with our security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所有的监控摄像头都被黑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of our surveillance cameras are being scrambled somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们在处理了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we're working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}要求传送地址\N端口号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来告诉你一些你们要找的人的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me tell you something about the man you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入中情局之前  他为五角大楼的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Before the CIA, he worked for the Pentagon for two years
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反间谍活动办公室工作过两年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the Counterintelligence Field Activities Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他了解那栋建筑的每一个角落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knows every single corner of that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们必须让摄像头工作起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to get those cameras up and running.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}状态  传送中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:20:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}完成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见了科克兰将军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I met with General Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他帮我从里士满的行政机构中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He helped me put together this list of staffers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整理出了这份名单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}inside of the Richmond Administration
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都符合我们谈及的条件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that fit the criteria we're talking about --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有高级权限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}high-level access,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并参与了选择指定幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}involvement in choosing the Designated Survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽快把这些资料给里特探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get these to Agent Ritter as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  我必须要说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, I do have to say --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有将军的帮忙我是无法完成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't have done this without the General's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他和袭击并无关联\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think he had anything to do with the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在追踪嫌疑人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In pursuit of suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正在前往乔治城铁路站场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}heading towards Georgetown Rail Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请求支援\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Send backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.57,0:26:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事还没结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.59,0:26:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.76,0:26:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有胜利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.41,0:26:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹尼斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dennis!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.94,0:26:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹尼斯应该开溜了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think Dennis stepped away.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.97,0:26:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗  作为看门人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, as far as gatekeepers go,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.09,0:26:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还差了点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's a lot to be desired here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.27,0:26:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你应该升升级了  赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think maybe it's time to trade up, Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.71,0:26:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, you should just move in at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.80,0:26:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是喜欢我现在这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I prefer the view from my side of the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.98,0:26:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎样  埃布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want, Abe?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.37,0:26:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你帮我转告总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look... I want you to tell the president
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.31,0:26:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的话我认真思考了很久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought long and hard about what he said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.65,0:27:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尊重他的要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to honor his request.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.16,0:27:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.57,0:27:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是无限期的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not indefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.42,0:27:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很意外  不知道该说什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm... speechless. I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.39,0:27:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为新闻发言人这水平可不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not the best quality for a press secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.59,0:27:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就说谢谢你吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, l-let me just say "thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.60,0:27:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.57,0:27:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别以为我这是示弱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't think for a second I'm going soft here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.35,0:27:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是会给你找麻烦的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll still be kicking your ass all over the schoolyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.84,0:27:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时奉陪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know where to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.17,0:27:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.18,0:27:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.33,0:27:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.68,0:27:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.75,0:27:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我送你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I get you a...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.58,0:27:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去医院吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.06,0:27:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是别的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.24,0:27:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们已经让我出院了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They already checked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.27,0:28:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道洛萨诺为什么去五角大楼了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you guys find out why Lozano was at the Pentagon yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.77,0:28:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我们能很快知道答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hopefully, we'll get answers soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.58,0:28:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.78,0:28:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要我留下来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you want me to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.65,0:28:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.33,0:28:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用  法索那边需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Foerstel needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.88,0:28:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过尽快跟我联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But check in as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.14,0:28:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.82,0:28:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以免我忘了  我并没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, before I forget -- I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.01,0:28:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想故意打探什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you know, snooping around or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.61,0:28:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你好像收到了很多电子邮件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you got about a thousand unread e-mails.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.87,0:28:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我一直忙着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I've been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.68,0:28:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一封是杰森·亚特伍德的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's one from Jason Atwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.07,0:28:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得应该告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you'd like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.59,0:28:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.15,0:29:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这项行动仍然有可行性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The operation is still viable.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.78,0:29:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  我会清除你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right now, I'm brooming any connection
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.22,0:29:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布朗宁·里德以及国会任务之间的联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}between you, Browning Reed, and the Capitol mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.93,0:29:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I want to know why there were
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.92,0:29:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么两名联调局调查员来调查我的物业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}two federal investigators on my property.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.91,0:29:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你别担心  我会去查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry about it. I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.47,0:29:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快  就不会再有书面记录等等的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon, there'll be no paper trail whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.71,0:29:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且威尔士探员已被抓获\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Agent Wells is contained.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.35,0:29:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都在按计划进行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything is proceeding as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.79,0:29:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you're sure
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.00,0:29:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局不会发现任何端倪吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the FBI has no idea what's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.34,0:29:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-控制权在我们手里  -那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We have operational control. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.84,0:29:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确保剧情会按照我们的剧本发展\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just make sure that the narrative is what we want it to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.68,0:29:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就快接近了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.36,0:29:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也许没有总统地位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We might not have the presidency,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.00,0:29:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可以十分肯定  不久以后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you can be damn sure that before long,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.93,0:29:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就能掌控整个国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we will have the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.97,0:29:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠特克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Whitaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.42,0:29:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能谈谈吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I have a word, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.36,0:30:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.32,0:30:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚特伍德副局长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deputy Director Atwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.75,0:30:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是汉娜·威尔士探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Agent Hannah Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.44,0:30:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  来自芝加哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes -- from Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.43,0:30:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅里特探员让我告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agent Merritt tells me to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.79,0:30:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是很生你的气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that he's still very pissed at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.82,0:30:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  我和他的看法不是总能达成一致的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, Agent Merritt and I didn't always see eye-to-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.25,0:30:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还跟我说你几乎违背了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He also tells me that you disobeyed
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.87,0:30:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他给你的下达的每一个命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}practically every order he gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.85,0:30:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不长官  我只违背那些值得违背的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, sir -- only the orders worth disobeying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.84,0:30:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还说  你是他手下最优秀的探员之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He also says that you were one of the best agents he's ever had,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.65,0:30:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是他对你的离开感到气愤的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is why he's mad at you for leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.59,0:30:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我说的  他是个很棒的上司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, like I was saying, he was a-a great boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.22,0:31:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔士探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agent Wells...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.37,0:31:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实话告诉我  你会给我带来麻烦吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in all honesty, will you cause me any trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.39,0:31:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Probably, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.16,0:31:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome to D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.54,0:31:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就快接近了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.22,0:31:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也许没有总统地位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We might not have the presidency,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.90,0:31:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可以十分肯定  不久以后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you can be damn sure that before long,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.79,0:31:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就能掌控整个国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we will have the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.84,0:31:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.93,0:31:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部的真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.71,0:31:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉我把你们蒙在鼓里这么久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am very sorry for keeping you in the dark for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.04,0:32:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I didn't feel like I had any other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.70,0:32:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你们能原谅我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you can forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.55,0:32:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.16,0:32:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Same here, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.65,0:32:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是惠特克让你成为的指定幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, Whitaker made you Designated Survivor?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.50,0:32:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  他以国土安全部顾问的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, as Homeland Security Advisor,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.23,0:32:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手握极佳的政治位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he was well-positioned
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.23,0:32:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为劳埃德执行了许多行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to carry out a number of operations for Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.34,0:32:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳埃德现在在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's Lloyd now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.56,0:32:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还在搜查当中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're still searching for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.79,0:32:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过作为世界上的头号通缉犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But as the most wanted man on the planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.42,0:32:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到他只是时间问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's just a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.35,0:32:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the meantime,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.06,0:32:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局突袭了他在全国各地的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the FBI raided cells from his organization
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.55,0:32:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基层组织\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}across the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.03,0:32:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕了超过二百人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They've arrested over 200 people,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.38,0:32:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缴获了枪支  制造炸弹的材料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}seizing firearms, bomb-making materials,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.15,0:32:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括与国会爆炸案中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}including explosives --
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.30,0:32:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用的同一种炸药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the same kind that were used at the Capitol bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.99,0:32:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.66,0:32:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候告诉美国民众事情的真相了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's time to tell the American people the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.92,0:32:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我会通知各大电视台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Absolutely -- - I'll inform the networks,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.75,0:32:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确保他们能排出档期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}make sure they clear some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.02,0:32:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我不想在总统办公室发表讲话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to speak from the Oval.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.19,0:32:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想发表国会演讲  召开联席会议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to address Congress -- a joint session.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.16,0:32:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you -- all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.58,0:32:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们所做的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.35,0:32:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去工作吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.78,0:32:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.19,0:33:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦  我能占用你一点时间吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aaron, can I borrow you for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.48,0:33:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.09,0:33:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are your plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.31,0:33:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在考虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm still figuring that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.26,0:33:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你回到白宫来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like you back here at the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.88,0:33:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你属于这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.18,0:33:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很感谢您的表态  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate the gesture, Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.89,0:33:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的职位已经有人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but... my position is been filled.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.94,0:33:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且艾米丽干得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Emily's doing a fantastic job.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.60,0:33:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全同意你的看法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't agree with you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.01,0:33:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会再给你找个职位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll find you another position.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.74,0:33:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  总统先生  没有这样的职位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Frankly, sir, none exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.68,0:33:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就造一个出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I'll make one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.27,0:33:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦  我想让你在这工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aaron, I want you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.68,0:33:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逼急了我拖也要把你拖过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll draft you if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.73,0:33:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不接受"不"这个回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I won't take "No" for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.75,0:33:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you say to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.88,0:33:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很愿意为总统效劳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I say I serve at the pleasure of the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.49,0:33:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.94,0:33:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为从法律意义上讲  我不能把你拖过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause legally, I actually don't think I can draft you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.80,0:33:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.12,0:33:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.96,0:33:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.50,0:33:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚准备好了没  要演讲了高兴吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ready for tonight? Happy with your speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.06,0:33:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好是准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I better be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.90,0:34:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是我自己写的稿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wrote it myself this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.29,0:34:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为你骄傲  年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm proud of you, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.68,0:34:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚坐在那看你演讲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm going to be even prouder
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.35,0:34:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会更骄傲的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when I watch you from my seat tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.89,0:34:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正想跟您谈谈这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to talk to you about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.77,0:34:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.44,0:34:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是那次袭击之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is gonna be - the first time since the attack
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.46,0:34:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有政府成员首次共聚一堂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the entire government will be under the same roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.13,0:34:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我要做出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I have to make a decision --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.65,0:34:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让谁留下来的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who to leave behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.47,0:34:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我心中做指定幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't think of anyone I would want more
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.69,0:34:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最合适的人选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to be my Designated Survivor than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.41,0:34:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前认为当指定幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I used to think that being Designated Survivor
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.05,0:34:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一种惩罚  一个玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was a punishment -- a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.77,0:34:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.83,0:34:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在不是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.84,0:34:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实不是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.64,0:34:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的荣幸  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would be my honor, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.81,0:34:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.76,0:35:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们  先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.32,0:35:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会成员们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}members of Congress,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.19,0:35:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的美国民众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my fellow Americans.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.50,0:35:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾在就任总统伊始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At the very beginning of my presidency,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.94,0:35:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个笼罩着恐怖阴霾的重要夜晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the shadow of that terrible, fateful night,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.05,0:35:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与你们讲过话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I spoke to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.69,0:35:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承诺过执政绝对透明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I promised absolute transparency,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.68,0:35:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对真实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}absolute truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.72,0:35:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我违背了那些誓言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I betrayed that pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.87,0:35:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为的是保护联调局和特勤局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in an effort to protect an ongoing investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.19,0:35:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在进行的调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by the FBI and the Secret Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.95,0:35:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今晚  我的心情异常轻松\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But tonight, I speak to you with a lightened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.77,0:35:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我终于能够把所有事实真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I can finally tell you the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.67,0:35:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉大家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about what really happened to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.55,0:35:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近一位受举国尊敬的记者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A recent article written
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.60,0:35:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写了一篇文章  他说的没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by one of our nation's most respected journalists was correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.76,0:35:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔萨卡没有袭击我们的国会大厦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Al-Sakar did not attack our Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.61,0:35:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使那个时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even though at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.58,0:35:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大量的证据都指向他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}overwhelming evidence suggested just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.69,0:35:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们可以百分百确定地告诉大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can tell you now, with absolute certainty,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.39,0:35:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场可怕的恐怖行动是由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that this horrific act was carried out
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.42,0:35:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国内的恐怖团伙策划的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by a domestic terror group,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.11,0:35:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领导者叫帕特里克·劳埃德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}led by a man named Patrick Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.84,0:36:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特里克和他的朋友认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lloyd and his followers believed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.44,0:36:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟大美国已经衰落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that American greatness was in its decline
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.52,0:36:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们认为我们不再是推翻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that somehow, we were no longer heirs
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.45,0:36:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法西斯主义和成功登月的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the generations that pushed back the tide of fascism,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.44,0:36:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那代人的继承者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}put men on the moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.06,0:36:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为我们把柏林墙精神遗弃在历史之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and relegated the Berlin Wall to the pages of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.37,0:36:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简而言之  这些人相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In short, these people believed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.54,0:36:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最好的时光已一去不复返\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that our best days were behind us
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.66,0:36:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他们  认为自己更懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that they, themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.19,0:36:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何重建我们的国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}knew better how to remake our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.22,0:36:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They were wrong --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.19,0:36:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错的非常离谱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in every possible way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.47,0:36:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们贬低了美国梦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They debased the American Dream and disrespected
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.43,0:36:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,践踏了无数个为保卫美国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the incredible sacrifices made by so many
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.43,0:36:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而牺牲的先烈们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to build and sustain our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.05,0:36:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就算美国国旗因为他们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And even though the fabric of America
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.46,0:36:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴力和仇恨有所磨损\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}may have been frayed by their violence and hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.75,0:36:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很开心有一个事实是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I stand here rejoicing in the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.54,0:36:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国旗绝不会因此而撕裂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that it was never torn.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.65,0:36:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使面临空前的恐惧  我们也没有抛弃彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a time of unprecedented fear, we did not abandon one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.95,0:36:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有抛弃我们的理想  我们的团结\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nor did we abandon our ideals, our sense of community,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.86,0:36:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our commonalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.18,0:37:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从在悲剧来临时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From the first responders who answered the call,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.07,0:37:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接到电话重进火海的急救人员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}racing into the flames when tragedy struck,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.22,0:37:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那些通过投票来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the men and women who fulfilled their civic duties
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.92,0:37:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,履行公民义务的所有群众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by casting their ballots
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.33,0:37:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使头顶袭击的威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even under the threat of attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.57,0:37:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人民的光芒依旧刺破苍穹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our better angels have shined through.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.13,0:37:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道有时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I know that there are times
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.64,0:37:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的国家显得四分五裂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when our country appears to be divided,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.75,0:37:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我能看到有一样东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I have seen the one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.03,0:37:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我们永远联系在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that will bind us together forever --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.59,0:37:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}love.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.54,0:37:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对祖国的爱  对希望和梦想的爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Love of country, love of hope, love of dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.48,0:37:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对生命的爱  对自由和追寻幸福的爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}love of life, liberty, and the pursuit of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.70,0:37:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是丈夫  是父亲  是这个国家的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am a husband, I am a father, and I am a son of this nation,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.09,0:37:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从未如此骄傲  如此乐观\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and never before have I been more proud, more optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.73,0:37:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不需要告诉我  你们深有同感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I do not need you to tell me that you feel the same way, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.82,0:37:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我能从你们的眼中看出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I can see it in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.10,0:37:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你们内心的声音里听出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and hear it in your hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.21,0:37:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如圣·保罗告诫我们的一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As Saint Paul admonished us,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.98,0:37:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我们不要被恶战胜  要以善胜恶"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Let us not be overcome by evil, but overcome evil with good."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.96,0:37:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国不只是一个国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see, America is not just simply a country,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.32,0:38:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是五十个州的简单集合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}nor is it the sum of its 50 states.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.68,0:38:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国是一种信念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an idea --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.43,0:38:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一种大胆而正义的信念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a bold and righteous idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.47,0:38:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一盏永不会熄灭的明灯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a guiding light that can never be extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.52,0:38:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们要对世界其他国家们说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So let us say to the rest of the world --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.92,0:38:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们期待你们的友好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we welcome your friendship and extend an open hand
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.75,0:38:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也向所有寻求自由美好生活的人们伸出双手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to anyone who wants to make lives freer and better.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.93,0:38:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而与我们为敌的人  我只能警告你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And to those who oppose us, I can only simply warn you --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.70,0:38:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们时日无多了  因为我们的时代来临了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your days are numbered, for our time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.67,0:38:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我重申  我们的时代来临了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I say again, our time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.61,0:38:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国人民们  请允许我说一句\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And to the American people, let me say
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.65,0:38:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能为你们服务是我毕生的荣耀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that it has been the privilege of my lifetime to serve you,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.62,0:38:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你们保证  我将继续努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I promise to continue serving
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.53,0:38:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到你们不再需要我为止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until I am asked of service no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.17,0:38:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你们给我的荣誉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for the honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.17,0:38:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝保佑你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.76,0:38:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝保佑美国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And God bless the United States of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.18,0:39:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.20,0:39:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.29,0:39:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们做的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.23,0:39:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.46,0:39:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Little pea!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.29,0:39:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  你怎么来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my gosh! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.05,0:39:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-李奥  -妈妈带我们来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Leo! - Mom brought us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.72,0:39:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在无法不让他们见你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't keep them away any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.88,0:39:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  我好想你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my gosh. I missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.74,0:39:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You look so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.62,0:39:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下  先生  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me, sir. Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.55,0:39:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  麦克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.31,0:39:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要您立刻到指挥行动中心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're needed in Command Ops right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.14,0:39:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证  马上就回来  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promise - I'll be right back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.49,0:39:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我爱你  -我也爱你  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I love you. - I love you, too, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.55,0:39:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.62,0:39:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.06,0:39:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.33,0:39:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-稍息  -是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- At ease. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.24,0:39:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.22,0:39:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我们知道洛萨诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, we know what Lozano
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.70,0:39:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在五角大楼拿到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was accessing at the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.05,0:39:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他黑进了国防部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He hacked the Defense Department's
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.32,0:40:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最高机密的服务器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}most highly classified server.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.58,0:40:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意味着什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.68,0:40:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意味着国家防御体系的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It means every single aspect
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.85,0:40:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一个环节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of our country's defense superstructure
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.61,0:40:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都有危险  军队调动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is now vulnerable -- troop movements,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.79,0:40:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核武器储备  秘密线人的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}intel on our nuclear arsenal, identities of our covert assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.90,0:40:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.35,0:40:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为洛萨诺把这些数据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We think that Lozano
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.81,0:40:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发给了帕特里克·劳埃德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sent the data to Patrick Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.46,0:40:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳埃德可能借此向我们索要赎金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lloyd could hold us to ransom,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.59,0:40:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把情报一点点卖给出价最高的买家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sell off the information in pieces to the highest bidder,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.14,0:40:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至自己将这些情报军事化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even militarize the intel himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.11,0:40:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他的追捕有进展吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are we any closer to finding him?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.98,0:40:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.56,0:40:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他手上握有的资源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He has the resources to get himself
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.91,0:40:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让他在不触发任何警报的情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}anywhere in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.78,0:40:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往世界任何地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without setting off any trip wires.
